        "description": "Transient ImmortalBuffTap-casting any skill will put Suyou in his Mortal form, grant him 40 Movement Speed and decreasing the interval between Basic Attacks.  Hold-casting any skill will put Suyou in his Immortal form, increasing the damage of Basic Attacks to 125% and granting him 20% Physical Damage Reduction. In this form, for every 20 extra Physical Attack Suyou has, he gains 1% Physical Damage Reduction (up to 40%). Icon variants Calculation t o t a l P h y s i c a l D M G r e d u c t i o n = ( 0.05 × e x t r a P h y s i c a l",
